### Export Products with Basic Attributes
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/export
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productIds": [1, 2, 3],
  "attributes": [
    "id",
    "name",
    "sku",
    "status"
  ],
  "format": "json",
  "filename": "basic_products_export.json"
}

