### Error Responses:

### Missing Product IDs
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/export
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productIds": [],
  "attributes": ["id", "name"]
}

# Response: 400 Bad Request
# {
#   "statusCode": 400,
#   "message": ["At least one product ID must be provided"],
#   "error": "Bad Request"
# }

###

### Missing Attributes
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/export
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productIds": [1, 2],
  "attributes": []
}

# Response: 400 Bad Request
# {
#   "statusCode": 400,
